{"tid":1154167,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【求婚成功】猷君深夜繼續high爆示愛 四太：「最快明年先搞婚禮」","createTime":"2019-05-14T06:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T07:55:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43ccc68f1d73db14abd9c2d8b30abb18bca48f08","tid":1154167,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"早被洩露風聲的猷君「求婚大典」，昨晚正式完成，24歲的猷君，於四太名下的上海尚嘉中心商場，將當中三層全封並進行布置，向年長6年的女友奚夢瑤求婚。猷君不但早已預備99,999朵玫瑰，更將場內布置成童話王國，擺放粉紅色拱門及城堡。<br />\n昨晚8時左右，現場已有過千名親朋戚友準備見證「大典」，猷君母親四太、家姐超盈等亦在場。猷君化身電玩遊戲中的「Mario」，而奚夢瑤則以粉紅色公主裝出現，之後奚夢瑤被奸角擄走，再由猷君主演英雄救美。<br />\n而最重要的求婚環節，則是猷君先在台上唱出《活著Viva》，之後換上全白色西裝，並以普通話、英語及廣東話向奚夢瑤說出：「我愛你」，並說：「Marry me？」，奚夢瑤開心點頭，而猷君則表現興奮。<br />\n成功抱得美人歸，猷君事後情緒依然高漲，深夜在微博上繼續發表愛的宣言，表示難以相信奚夢瑤成為他的妻子，再問到未來的童話生活會如何，並話仍未相信自己已訂婚。奚夢瑤事後亦在社交網上載求婚相片，並留言說：「I said YES!!!!!!Of course I did!!!!!!!!!! 」表現同樣興奮。而四太則向傳媒表示，今年屬盲年，加上籌備需時，所以猷君的婚禮，最快也要明年才可舉行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190514/large/1557807893_b8b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557807893_b8b6.jpg&h=64ab2afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190514/large/1557807894_90ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557807894_90ec.jpg&h=2837a65a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190514/large/1557807895_4f94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557807895_4f94.jpg&h=41ba8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190514/large/1557807896_0a01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557807896_0a01.jpg&h=4a363060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190514/large/1557807898_500a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557807898_500a.jpg&h=c2778e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_669465_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_669465_0&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=0e8d8226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_669465_0&h=223d1be2\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_669465_0</a>"},{"pid":"973195c17f5518a4ca3ae97a5721329f5a03c8ec","tid":1154167,"uid":213517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 最後果張相成條撚咁反轉左"},{"pid":"3d81e8161d79cc41187fb2e7b866e0f5e4990c93","tid":1154167,"uid":82853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"下年先結婚 趕唔趕得切同賭王沖喜呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f7587723bebf3c6f66ad3aa29bbf09dbeae5f1","tid":1154167,"uid":6946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"需咩時丫, 等老豆就唔得再即刻行禮沖喜咋掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}